OL,3,CNewport Marathon organisers issue
OL,4,Capology after course distance was too
OL,5,Clong
OL,7,FNewport Marathon organisers have
OL,8,Fapologised after it was found the
OL,9,Fcourse of this year's race was too
OL,10,Flong.
OL,12,FThe race, which took place on April
OL,13,F28, was 276 metres longer than the
OL,14,F26.2 mile marathon distance - the
OL,15,Fequivalent to 0.171 miles.
OL,17,FRun 4 Wales says it is "disappointed
OL,18,Fthat this has happened at one of its
OL,19,Fevents and understands and apologies
OL,20,Funreservedly to those impacted".
