OL,7,FIn a statement posted on their social
OL,8,Fmedia pages, the organisers said:
OL,9,F"We've been looking into reports
OL,10,Faround the accuracy of the marathon
OL,11,Fcourse distance at the Newport
OL,12,FMarathon Festival on Sunday 28 April.
OL,14,F"This issue has been taken very
OL,15,Fseriously and we have been having an
OL,16,Fongoing dialogue with the Course
OL,17,FMeasurer/Association of UK Course
OL,18,FMeasurers (AUKCM).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
