OL,7,FIn a statement, the Association of UK
OL,8,FCourse Measurers (AUKCM) said they are
OL,9,Ftaking the reports "very seriously."
OL,11,FMike Burns, AUKCM Secretary, said:
OL,12,F"Without a verification check on the
OL,13,Fcourse we are unable to confirm the
OL,14,Fexact details of any measurement
OL,15,Ferror. However, a detailed inspection
OL,16,Fof the measurement report (which runs
OL,17,Fto 20 pages) confirms a likely error
OL,18,Fat one point in the course.
