OL,7,F"AUKCM certifies over 2000 races a
OL,8,Fyear and we sincerely regret where any
OL,9,Fissues of accuracy arise. Fortunately,
OL,10,Fthese are very few and the majority
OL,11,Fare dueJto issues outside the control
OL,12,Fof AUKCM."
